Title: Sharif Returns
Plot: When the NCIS team learns that the missing 10 kilograms of highly toxic chemical weapons are now in the hands of Mamoun Sharif, a wanted terrorist, they will have to find a way to find the man and stop him before it's too late with the aid from Army Lt. Col. Hollis Mann and constant phone calls from Sharif himself.
GuestStars: Susanna Thompson, Enzo Cilenti, Scottie Thompson, Victor Webster, David Starzyk, Rob Brownstein, David Barrera
